.SH "NAME"
linuxcnctop \- live LinuxCNC status description
.SH "SYNOPSIS"
.sp
\fBlinuxcnctop\fR \fB\-ini\fR \fIINIFILE\fR
.SH "DESCRIPTION"
.sp
\fBlinuxcnctop\fR displays much of the LinuxCNC state in a live format similar to the Linux "top" command\&.
.sp
It is more fully documented in the AXIS GUI documentation but can be run standalone or with other GUIs\&.
